<h2 style="text-align: center;">Dealing With A Dangerous Student</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>Anyone that comes in contact with or encounters a dangerous student</em></p>
<p><em>&nbsp;</em><em>that is <span style="text-decoration: underline;">threatening bodily harm</span> (hostage taker, kidnapper, suicidal subject) should take the following action:</em></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Call 911</span> and ask for police to respond.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Leave the area</span> if you can do so safely.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If you cannot leave, attempt to <span style="text-decoration: underline;">keep them calm</span> until emergency personnel arrive.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Do not engage</span> in controversial or threatening conversation.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Do not</span> attempt to <span style="text-decoration: underline;">physically restrain</span> them unless they are actively attempting to harm themselves or another person.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If they are armed, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">comply with their requests</span> if at all possible.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Have an <span style="text-decoration: underline;">escape route</span> in mind in the event they begin to carry out their threats.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Wait for police</span> to arrive and take them into custody if they appear to be in imminent danger of harming themselves or others.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">A<em>nyone that comes in contact with or becomes aware of an <span style="text-decoration: underline;">active shooter</span> in the vicinity should take the following action:</em></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If at all possible <span style="text-decoration: underline;">get away,</span> provided you can move without being seen by the shooter.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If you cannot flee, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">take cover</span>, hide as best you can.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Make your <span style="text-decoration: underline;">room appear to be unoccupied</span> turn off lights, pull blinds, lock doors.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Time permitting, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">barricade</span> your area by placing heavy objects in front of doors if the door opens into the room you are hiding in. Cover windows so you cannot be seen.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Maintain silence</span>, do not talk, silence your cell phone.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; When rescue arrives <span style="text-decoration: underline;">follow police instructions precisely</span>.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If you are detected by the shooter and he attacks, prepare to <span style="text-decoration: underline;">attack the shooter</span> as a group or individually if necessary.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x9764" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x9287" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl" Expanded="fals